lerics spamming group heals and PALLIES (yes, pallies own) spamming WoH/HWoP keeps people alive... <br>
<br>
Her melee is nada, her AE is everything. Also try to beef up yer FR, I know that the AE is resistable (i've resisted it a couple times), although VERY hard to resist.. Btw, the AE is actually 1500 damage... 500 damage over 3 ticks dot (hence, the 18 seconds) and as soon as it would have worn off, she AEs again. However, I've heard that each TICK is actually resistable, cuz it's a kindy funky dot. Meaning, it could land on you, but only end up doing 1000 or even 500 damage, rather than always doin the full 1500.<br>
<br>
